name: Fratelli's Hideout - aka Lighthouse Lounge
description: Analog 35mm film photograph of the Fratelli's Hideout from the film The Goonies (1985). Located in Ecola State Park, this film location is just a park shelter, but was built up as set decoration for shots in the film. Shot on a vintage Canon AE-1 using Portra 400 film. 3130 x 2175 px scan from original negative
